OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchool leaders' union could
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftake Ofsted to court       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ofsted could face a legal challenge    
OL,6, over its decision not to pause its     
OL,7, school inspections after the death of  
OL,8, head teacher Ruth Perry.               
OL,10,FMs Perry took her own life while       
OL,11,Fwaiting for a report that downgraded   
OL,12,Fher school to "inadequate".            
OL,14,FThe NAHT school leaders' union wants   
OL,15,FEngland's schools watchdog to pause    
OL,16,Finspections so a review to cut the risk
OL,17,Fof harm to school staff can take place.
OL,19,FOfsted has said pausing inspections    
OL,20,Fwould not be good for children.        
